### Install RxDB and Supabase JS Client

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/replication-supabase.html

Installs the RxDB library and the official Supabase JavaScript client using npm. These are the core dependencies required for setting up the synchronization between RxDB and Supabase.

```bash
npm install rxdb @supabase/supabase-js
```

