### Enable `toggleOnDocumentVisible` for RxDB Replication (Experimental)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/replication.html

Configures RxDB replication to actively run when the browser tab is visible, even if it was previously in a hibernated state. This experimental feature helps prevent replication staleness in browsers that aggressively manage tab activity. The replication pauses automatically if visibility is lost and resumes when the tab becomes visible or regains leader status.

```javascript
const replicationState = replicateRxCollection({
    toggleOnDocumentVisible: true,
    /* ... */
});
```

